Create a wordpress website with mysql server.
Conditions:
- both service should be run in same container
- do not use any pre-container images and do installations manually
- start the service as foreground and mysql as background
- port should be exposed as 8083
- when login to the container the current directory should be /root
- both service should not have any manual configuration by gui only through with Shell script.
- mount the mysql database in the host machine while creating the container.
